<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3711] small SentinelIntSet can cause infinite loop on resize</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3711</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;A small initial size of &amp;lt;=4 can cause the set to not rehash soon enough and thus go into an infinite loop searching the table for an open space.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12539069">LUCENE-3711</key>
            <summary>small SentinelIntSet can cause infinite loop on resize</summary>
